          <ul class="list-content" id="our-research-menu"><li class="toplevel"><p><a href="http://www.cancerresearchuk.org/our-research/our-research-by-cancer-type" class="level2">By cancer type</a></p><ul><li><a href="http://www.cancerresearchuk.org/our-research/our-research-by-cancer-type/our-research-on-brain-tumours" class="level3">Brain tumours</a></li><li><a href="http://www.cancerresearchuk.org/our-research/our-research-by-cancer-type/our-research-on-skin-cancer" class="level3">Skin cancer</a></li><li><a href="http://www.cancerresearchuk.org/our-research/our-research-by-cancer-type/our-research-on-breast-cancer" class="level3">Breast cancer</a></li><li><a href="http://www.cancerresearchuk.org/our-research/our-research-by-cancer-type" class="level3">All cancer types</a></li>
        </ul></li><li class="toplevel"><p><a href="http://www.cancerresearchuk.org/our-research/our-research-by-cancer-subject" class="level2">By cancer subject</a></p><ul><li><a href="http://www.cancerresearchuk.org/our-research/our-research-by-cancer-subject/our-research-on-clinical-trials" class="level3">New treatments</a></li><li><a href="http://www.cancerresearchuk.org/our-research/our-research-by-cancer-subject/our-research-on-cancer-biology" class="level3">Cancer biology</a></li><li><a href="http://www.cancerresearchuk.org/our-research/our-research-by-cancer-subject/our-research-on-cancer-drugs" class="level3">Cancer drugs</a></li><li><a href="https://www.cancerresearchuk.org/our-research/our-research-by-cancer-subject" class="level3">All cancer subjects</a></li>
